Net-Limesco version 1.0
=======================

This module provides a Perl interface to the Limesco API at
http://api.limesco.org/.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires Carp (tested against version 1.17), JSON (tested against
version 2.53) and LWP::UserAgent (tested against version 6.03).

